                            <strong>Yoshua Bengio and Team Introduce GNN Benchmarking Framework</h3></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
