    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">The research team has released the open benchmark infrastructure for GNNs on <a href="https://github.com/graphdeeplearning/" target="_self">GitHub</a> based on PyTorch and DGL. The paper <em>Benchmarking Graph Neural Network </em>is on <a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/2003.00982.pdf" target="_self">arXiv</a>.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
